---
title: Classic Beef & Creamy Parmesan Sauce with Mash & Roasted Veggies
description: In this jazzed up version of meat and three veg, the creamy Parmesan sauce livens up the tender beef strips, while the roasted
veggies imparts a slightly sweet and earthy flavour to the overall dish. Serve with a smooth mash to keep things filling and to
soak up all that sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/classic-beef-creamy-parmesan-sauce-b72c7f71.jpg
